Package logic

Class Order

java.lang.Object
logic.Order
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Order extends Object implements Serializable
The Order class represents an order made by a visitor in the park management system. It contains various attributes related to the order, such as park name, order number, visitor ID, visitor type, date, time, number of visitors, contact details, exit time, total cost, payment status, and order status.
